  <div id="block-menu-block-stanford-jumpstart-layouts-2" class="clearfix block block-menu-block">     <h2><a href="/guidelines-and-standards" title="Overview of accessibility guidelines and standards." class="active-trail active">Guidelines / Standards</a></h2>
      <div class="content"> <div class="menu-block-wrapper menu-block-stanford_jumpstart_layouts-2 menu-name-main-menu parent-mlid-0 menu-level-2">
  <ul class="menu nav"><li class="first leaf menu-mlid-1155"><a href="/guidelines-standards/w3c-web-content-accessibility-guidelines-wcag-20">W3C Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG 2.0)</a></li>
<li class="last leaf menu-mlid-1187"><a href="/guidelines-standards/understanding-wcag-20">Understanding WCAG 2.0</a></li>
</ul></div>
